Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:27.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(307.429,306.571)\fnPaete Round\fs30}I'M NOT ALONE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.87,0:01:33.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,John... it's time for me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jules Verne...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I liked it too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:08.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Father, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,That's bad, I'm late for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I'll go now, your breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What about my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:25.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has been at Hamilton's\Nsince yesterday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:26.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing happened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:32.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What? Haven't been born yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:38.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Oh, today I'll return late,\Nso take care of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Your mother will be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, a boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:45.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Hamilton's baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:55.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,If this happens, I will take him\Nto the hill of the Rocky Heath!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:00.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:17.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning, Sam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning, Ed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kevin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, I rely on you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,How are you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:54.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,This is the best way to make delicious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,No one is answering to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:28.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful, John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm leaving!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I remembered, before I go to school...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:51.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?\NThis is not the road to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I haven't said "Good morning" to my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to Mrs. Hamilton!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:58.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:14.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Melissa, your son came!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, I can't talk to him, I'm working!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:24.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you saying, Mrs. Carraclough?\NYou mustn't make your son leave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Doctor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:33.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Well, good morning!\NHave you eaten your breakfast today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my father made it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:43.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Is not obstetrics difficult for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Difficulty is because of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,The night is gone and the child is not born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Well okay... wait a little, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mrs. Carraclough! Please help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:01.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,When the child is born, I will return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:27.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:36.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brad Hamilton's baby was born recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,She's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,She's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Congratulations, you became a father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of going to the river\Nbefore we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:18.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to go, but I have work in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:24.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Well okay, my mom will be home\Nin the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:29.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,The river, you say? Do you want\Nto play there again until you get muddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you speak as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,No, I will not go to the river again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:35.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Well... it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:07.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:13.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Mom, haven't you come home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Is she sleeping on the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Oh, John, you are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:45.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, the child is born yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:50.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes, when your father told me the news,\NI came right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,The ladies who also helped have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:56.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Now come and see our child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:57.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:00.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, where is my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:04.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Well, she left with Dr. Hooper, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,And now, this way! This way, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,You see? Her eyebrows are very beautiful,\Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:16.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful to your mother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:33.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hello John!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:37.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,You act like a little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh sorry, but I have to go out again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger has been infected with peritonitis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,He needs a procedure, so I have\Nto take care of him all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,But, Mom, you haven't slept last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is skilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,But John, can you have dinner alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:03.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? You are already a big boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:08.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Well, I prepared the food for you\Nand put it on the dish so you can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Colin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,John?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hello Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I told you before that I can't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:37.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I know that! Are you going\Nto deliver the goods? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,It seems difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:51.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that way I can walk around\Nwith you, Colin, all over the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:56.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,If I let you ride this bike, I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:01.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,To move around the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happens to me\Nif it's damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:09.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go with Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I'm alone again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no other choice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's an airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:41.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, I would like\Nto fly with this plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,It's landing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stay away of this bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:36.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey don't do that! This is not mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,How long will they continue to walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:03.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here? This is the?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! You will be crushed if you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:28.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,You, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Well... well, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:31.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Don't approach the sheep again,\Nyou will be crushed if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Go home quickly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:40.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I have to deliver these immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Ah ah, I am tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I have to go home and have dinner alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, hey? Are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a home to go back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Could you be sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:05.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll take you home immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Colin! I finished the delivery!\NYour bike is outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:23.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Faster! Faster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Look, I lit the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Come here and warm by the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:53.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,My mother often come back late,\Nso I know how to light it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Do you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:06.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Great smell, dinner made by my mother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,You, could you be hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:13.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,This... this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What? There is no milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm going to fetch milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:46.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what color is the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:48.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:52.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,It's covered in brown,\Nand also it has white.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,It's this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,So it's still a puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:01.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Listen, next time I'll see the puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's milk! It's delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:29.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter? Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:39.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?\NCan't you drink milk by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Like a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:46.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired, I want my father\Ncome back quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Okay here you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,There are two men that haven't yet ascended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Time has already passed....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I hope there wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:19.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What is that? It's still a puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:23.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Colin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:31.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John! Is it you, John?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Sorry John, my father scolded me a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "thank you" for delivery to John?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,This is because you were busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, do you have a child's bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Child's bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,- A puppy?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last child's bottle was sold to Mrs. Hamilton.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Ah wait! I have one from my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:04.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Next time I'll see the puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Can it drink through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,You're very hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,You've already finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What is that?\NYour mood has changed completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You feel better, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I arrived late...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,You do extra work, Sam Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,There were two men I didn't see,\Nso I rushed to look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I found them relaxing inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today Hamilton had a baby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,What about your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:09.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,Poor one is still asleep alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:13.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,No, I know, I'm going to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,John, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:18.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,John?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:22.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,You wait until I get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder where it came from?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:43.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,I understand, you are no longer alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:02.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While I went to school\NI left the puppy at home, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of that, it brought mess in the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:07.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:11.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NA BIG MESS AT HOME{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:12.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look forward to that!{\i0}
